After the reopening of a comptoir in Biarritz in 2016, Maison @Goyard continues along its path in search of lost time, and very pleased to announce the opening of a comptoir in Monte Carlo in 2018 #Goyard #MonteCarlo #Heritage #History #NewComptoir #Soon

At the turn of the 20th century, Maison @Goyard was operating comptoirs in three cities: Paris, Biarritz and Monte Carlo. As a nod to this beloved past, the tag on our trunks still mentions the three locations, although the two latter closed in the 1930s https://t.co/Um4C0MeIVU
